Notation
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Notation will be different between calibration and prediction models because
 the calibration model uses only one pollen count vector per site while
 the prediction model has multiple count vectors per site.
 In the calibration model, let 
\begin_inset Formula $j=1,...,J$
